Question -1

Write a shell program to calculate the factorial of a number.


Code -

read -p "enter a no to calculate the factorial of a number: " num
f=1
while [ $num -gt 1 ]
do
f=$((fact*num))
num=$((num-1))
done
echo $fact

Important Instruction-

1. To run above code you need the linx 
2. In that open the terminal 
3. write the gedit (fileName).sh
4. Now write the code
5. to Run the code sh (fileName).sh

